8 units嚗�
1.	Introduction of maritime archeology: Explain the definition, area and scope of maritime archeology, and clarify the difference between the maritime archeology and underwater archeology, between maritime archeology and underwater treasure seeking. Moreover, introduce the museums related to maritime archeology in many countries.
2.	Development and achievements of western maritime archeology VS Mediterranean maritime civilization.
3.	Development and achievements of western maritime archeology VS Atlantic maritime civilization.
4.	Western achievements and eastern introduction of maritime archeology.
5.	Development and achievements of maritime archeology in the countries surrounding the China Sea.
